NAWIA GAMES - Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
NAWIA GAMES Sp. z o.o. ("Nawia") does not obtain, collect and process any personal data in the sense of the GDPR standards.
Other data, that is collected implicitly, impersonally and anonymously while using Nawia's Service, may include:
Service information
Nawia may collect information about your installation, such us the operating system type and application version number.
Device information
Nawia may collect device-specific information, such as hardware platform and operating system version.
Third-party services
Nawia may use third-party services to be able to understand the use of its sole Service, such as Google Analytics or Facebook Analytics. These third-party service providers may collect information sent by your browser as part of a web page request, such as cookies or your IP address, as well as in-game events.
Nawia may use third-party services to provide ads in its Products. The ads suppliers may use Service Information, Device Information or other specific, obtainable information (such as IDFA), to personalize ads to the end user. The ad tracking can be limited via privacy settings on the particular device.
Third-party services providers' privacy policies can be reviewed below:
AdMob:
https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543?hl=en&ref_topic=2745287
AppLovin:
https://www.applovin.com/gdprfaqs
Unity Ads:
https://unity3d.com/legal/gdpr
Nawia processes your non-private, aggregated or otherwise non-personal information (commonly known as "usage statistics") to constantly improve Nawia's Service.
